Constant-rate birth death
========================================================

```{r}
tree <- pbtree(
  b = 0.2,
  d = 0.1,
  n = 10,
  extant.only = TRUE
)
```

```{r eval=FALSE}
plot.phylo(
  tree,
  edge.width = 1,
  cex = 2
)
```
***
```{r echo=FALSE}
